Lunarpine awoke, his arm healed from his tag match with Shadow Wing. 
He was programmed for night so he decided to step out. "Personal 
message for any command personell, This is Lunarpine, I'm going on a 
recon mission, I saw some cliffs not to far to the southeast, they 
might make a good lookout post." he ended his message and headed for 
the door."Autoguns deactivate, remember my signature when I return." 
He transformed to wolf and headed out.

About a mile out he caught a scent on the wind."Whats Shadow Wing 
doing out?" he didn't see her logout code." She's probably mad I ate 
her dinner earlier. She's probably practicing to beat me next time." 
Lunarpine admired her for her dedication, but he fealt she needed 
another lesson and started to follow her scent.
(Anybody thinks I'm modeing by following her check Lunarpine on the 
character page,.)
